headline: AST SpaceMobile and Cadence Collaborate to Advance the World’s First and Only Planned Space-Based Global Cellular Broadband Network
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif. & MIDLAND, Texas, December 03, 2024--Cadence and AST SpaceMobile collaborated on the AST5000 ASIC, a custom, low-power architecture that leverages advanced Cadence tools, flows and IP.
